736 0 obj
<<
/Type /StructElem
/S /H1
/P 183 0 R
/T (12. Additional Features Land Ownership Land claims establish property rights. Claimed land is protected from others' modifications. Property can be bought, sold, shared, or transferred. Governments can establish public property. Power Systems Advanced technology requires power. The game models mechanical power \(mills, engines\) and electrical power \(generators, grids\). Power generation, transmission, and consumption create engineering challenges. Transportation Vehicles from hand carts to trucks enable bulk transport. Roads provide speed bonuses. Late game includes boats and potentially aircraft. Infrastructure investment pays off through efficiency gains. Research and Knowledge Technology requires research investment. Discovered knowledge persists in society even if researchers leave. This creates collective progress that transcends individual participants.)
/E (12. Additional Features Land Ownership Land claims establish property rights. Claimed land is protected from others' modifications. Property can be bought, sold, shared, or transferred. Governments can establish public property. Power Systems Advanced technology requires power. The game models mechanical power \(mills, engines\) and electrical power \(generators, grids\). Power generation, transmission, and consumption create engineering challenges. Transportation Vehicles from hand carts to trucks enable bulk transport. Roads provide speed bonuses. Late game includes boats and potentially aircraft. Infrastructure investment pays off through efficiency gains. Research and Knowledge Technology requires research investment. Discovered knowledge persists in society even if researchers leave. This creates collective progress that transcends individual participants.)
/Pg 41 0 R
/K [0]
>>
endobj
737 0 obj
<<
