738 0 obj
<<
/Type /StructElem
/S /P
/P 184 0 R
/E (Societies represents a new approach to multiplayer simulation games. By treating AI agents as first-class citizens equivalent to human players, the game solves fundamental problems that plague purely human-driven simulations: server death, economic stagnation, tedium requirements, and weak endgame.)
/Pg 42 0 R
/K [1]
>>
endobj
